@startuml
participant User
participant API
participant TaskStore
participant Worker
participant EC2
participant SES

User -> API: POST /launch
API -> API: Validate
API -> TaskStore: create_task()
TaskStore --> API: task_id
API --> User: 202 Accepted
API -> Worker: asyncio.create_task()

Worker -> EC2: run_instances()
EC2 --> Worker: instance_id
Worker -> TaskStore: update_task()
Worker -> SES: send_email()
@enduml
